text: Matthew Ebden and Andrew Whittington were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Sriram Balaji and Jonathan Erlich won the title after defeating Sander Arends and Tristan-Samuel Weissborn 6–3, 6–2 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Santaizi ATP Challenger - Doubles 2019 Doubles
